article_title: Viral Video: Tian Tian Plays In The Snow - News9.com - Oklahoma City, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports
article_text:
Tian Tian rolled around and frolicked in the deep snowfall.

Panda cub Bei Bei was not impressed with the snow National Zoo caretakers placed in his den Saturday. The cub walked through the bucket of snow for only a moment before snacking on some bamboo.

His father on the other hand had a blast in his habitat!

Tian Tian rolled around and frolicked in the deep snowfall.

He is kept in a separate habitat from his young cub and its mother.
